	Buss, D.M., Haselton, M.G., Shackelford, T.K., Bleaske, A.L., & wakefield,
J.C.  (1998).  Adaptations, Exaptations, and Spandrels.  American Psychologist, 53(5), 533-48.  

	Buss, D.M. and Shackelford, T.K. (1997).  From Vigilance to Violence: Mate
